value.string: To convert Geico sample file into template file
Bot reads all the required values from the Geico sample file
Convert the read values into required format and store in the standard template form.
In case of failure while finding/entering to a field, ERROR flag will be raised and BOT may be stopped

Agency Number,SSN/EIN,Firm (Agency) Name,Last Name,First name,Date of Birth,Home State License Number,License Expiration Date,Residence Street Address,City,State,ZIP,Business Street Address,City,State,ZIP,Appointment State,Appointed Y/N,AgencyEIN,Email,HorisonId,NEW/EXISTING,
---------Get Prefix value for HorisonID based on Residence State.
---------Get Residence Address Details based on Agency Number
